data.name: label6.Text
data.value: The Honda Activa is a motor scooter made by Honda Motorcycle and Scooter India (HMSI). It was launched in India in May 1999. It is a 109/125 cc, 7 bhp (5.2 kW) scooter. The vehicle has the option of kick- and self-start.

data.name: label7.Text
data.value: The TVS Apache RTR 160 is powered by a 159.7cc air-cooled, single-cylinder engine with a maximum power output of 15bhp at 8,500rpm and a peak torque output of 13.1Nm at 4,000rpm. The engine is coupled to a 5-speed gearbox. The engine has a punchy power delivery with the meat of the torque available at just 4,000rpm.
